Key Match Events: Tanzid Hasan came on as a concussion substitute for Soumya Sarkar after he hurt his neck while fielding.
Jaker Ali collided with Anamul Haque while attempting a catch, both sustaining injuries.
Mustafizur Rahman was stretchered off due to cramps, and Mushfiqur Rahim suffered a finger injury during the match.
Others: The match saw multiple injuries and substitutions, including the use of a concussion substitute and the withdrawal of an umpire due to heat.
